# Frontend Specifications

## Pre-Development Checklist

Before starting frontend work, read:

- [ ] `component-patterns.md` - Component design patterns and best practices
- [ ] `state-management.md` - State management patterns
- [ ] `styling.md` - Styling conventions and theme usage
- [ ] `accessibility.md` - Accessibility requirements and testing
- [ ] `testing.md` - Frontend testing strategies

