## Overview

This directory contains frontend-specific specifications and patterns.

## Contents

- **component-patterns.md** - Component structure, props patterns, composition
- **state-management.md** - Local state, global state, data fetching
- **styling.md** - CSS conventions, theme system, responsive design
- **accessibility.md** - ARIA labels, keyboard navigation, screen reader support
- **testing.md** - Component tests, integration tests, visual regression

